spells.description: Use: Conjure a Spectral Scythe, dealing 1.1 million Shadow damage to your target and 164,492 Shadow damage in a 15 yd cone to enemies behind your target. (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)

Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 2 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 98,867  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Taking damage greater than 25% of your health grants you 2,602 Avoidance and increases healing taken by 10% for 10 sec. This effect may only occur every 90 sec.

Falling damage reduced.

Equip: Gain Ascendance every 8 seconds spent in combat.

Ascendance grants 89 of a random secondary stat for 15 sec, stacking up to 10 times.

This is a Nerubian embellishment.
